    "description": "Join the Capital Float family as a Senior Software Engineer in Vadodara. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Capital Float:\nCapital Float is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Learning & development budget\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Capital Float!",
